<h1><b>JustChess.org</b></h1>

<p><b>A multiplayer chess server started in 2024 by Artem Bielikov</b></p>

<h3>Features:</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Match history</li>
  <li>Glicko-2 rating system</li>
  <li>Skill-based matchmaking</li>
  <li>Multiple concurrent games</li>
</ul>

